##########adduser


<How to add user in kali>

sudo adduser jeetu ( iske baad enter krna hai)

###for check

first go to root directory

cd /

sudo cat /etc/passwd

Some time it will show error msg like (<username> is not in the sudoers file)

##Solution >> login root as command 

su root 
nano /etc/sudoers

Scroll down until you find root  ALL=(ALL)  
ALL and add the following line below it. Replace <username> with your actual user name.
<your username> ALL=(ALL) ALL

then reboot command use

then again login . Now you can just type 

cat /etc/passwd 

###happy hacking
